WEBVTT

00:00.390 --> 00:01.780
Savant syndrome?

00:02.160 --> 00:03.560
Am I sick?

00:03.560 --> 00:06.420
I didn't say it's about you, Lain.

00:06.420 --> 00:09.310
Only that there are people who suffer from that sickness.

00:10.020 --> 00:11.620
If it's not about me...

00:11.620 --> 00:13.330
then why are talking about it?

00:13.860 --> 00:18.410
There are other children who may learn from your example.

00:20.010 --> 00:21.310
I'm only myself.

00:21.620 --> 00:23.000
Not other children.

00:25.010 --> 00:26.000
That's true!

00:26.910 --> 00:28.300
I'm sorry, Lain.

00:32.900 --> 00:34.130
What's wrong, Lain?

00:34.710 --> 00:36.510
Why are you calling me Lain?

00:39.780 --> 00:41.580
Who are you?
